					<i class="fa fa-user"></i>
					講員：					<a href="/speaker/view/162">董家驊牧師</a>
				</span>
				<span>
					<i class="fa fa-calendar-alt"></i>
					屆別:					<a href="/sermon/view?serial_no=97">第97屆</a>
